-- Nike sees Q4, FY sales up in high single digits
-- 
-- Thu Mar 22, 2007 5:28pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/03/22/us-nike-outlook-idUSN2244887420070322

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - Nike Inc. ( NKE.N ) Chief Financial Officer Don Blair said on Thursday he expects sales to rise in the high single digits on a percentage basis for both the fourth quarter and year. 

 The company's gross margins are expected to be at or slightly below year-ago levels for the fourth quarter and year, Blair added. Blair gave the forecast during a conference call with analysts to discuss the company's third-quarter results.